[13/10/2017 15:53:38] <font color="#00ff00">"Saber y ganar",</font>
[13/10/2017 15:53:41] <font color="#00ff00">un programa presentado</font>
[13/10/2017 15:53:41] <font color="#00ff00">por Jordi Hurtado.</font>
