[13/10/2017 22:32:12] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Toma, arsa!</font>
[13/10/2017 22:32:21] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Ole!</font>
[13/10/2017 22:32:31] <font color="#0000ff">Venganza...</font>
[13/10/2017 22:32:37] <font color="#0000ff">...es lo que tú te mereces,...</font>
[13/10/2017 22:32:44] <font color="#0000ff">...que cumpliera mi venganza,...</font>
[13/10/2017 22:32:52] <font color="#0000ff">...pero prefiero la muerte...</font>
[13/10/2017 22:33:00] <font color="#0000ff">...a vivir sin esperanza.</font>
