[13/10/2017 22:42:01] <font color="#ffffff">-Exagerado.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:07] <font color="#00ff00">Buenas noches, maestro Mairena.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:07] <font color="#00ff00">Soy Lucas.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:09] <font color="#00ff00">Y a veces, acompaño a ese.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:11] <font color="#ffffff">-Quita, no seas pesado, hombre.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:14] <font color="#ffffff">-No es tan malo, el jodido.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:16] <font color="#ffffff">-Bah.</font>
[13/10/2017 22:42:24] <font color="#0000ff">...que me aliviara...</font>
